<h4 id="nonparametric-statistics">Nonparametric statistics</h4>
<p>One of the biggest problems with tests like the chi-squared test is that they make a lot 
of assumptions about how your data was generated. Often we could figure out that this is 
without having to make a bunch of assumptions .</p>

